text: Zhongli (Chinese: 钟离) is a fictional character from the video game Genshin Impact. He is a Wangsheng Funeral consultant in the fictional country of Liyue, which is based off of China. During the Liyue main quest, it is revealed that he is the Geo Archon Morax. As of March 2021, the character Zhongli was the character who made the most money, with $15.5M. Raiden Shogun, another character from the game, is in second place at $9M. ==References== Category:Video game characters
